    "description": "Celebi India International Enterprises is actively seeking a talented and motivated Guest Relations Manager to join our dynamic team in Pimpri-Chinchwad. This is an excellent opportunity for professionals who are passionate about making a real impact in a fast-growing organization.\n\nAbout Celebi India International Enterprises:\nCelebi India International Enterprises is a leading organization in the Hybrid sector, committed to excellence, innovation, and employee growth. We offer a dynamic work environment where talent is recognized and rewarded.\n\nKey Responsibilities:\n• Monitor F&B service quality and maintain hygiene standards\n• Prepare daily operating reports and present to management\n• Assist in menu planning, costing, and food festival coordination\n• Manage front office operations including check-in/check-out\n• Deliver exceptional guest experiences in line with brand standards\n• Handle guest complaints and resolve issues promptly\n• Manage procurement of hotel supplies and control operating costs\n\nRequired Skills & Qualifications:\n• B.Sc / M.Sc in Life Sciences\n• 3-6 years of relevant experience\n• Proficiency in Housekeeping Standards\n• Proficiency in Event Management\n• Proficiency in OTA Management\n• Proficiency in Sommelier Skills\n• Proficiency in GDS Systems\n• Proficiency in Customer Relations\n• Proficiency in MICE\n• Proficiency in Yield Management\n\nWork Mode: Hybrid - Flexible work-from-home and office\n\nWhat We Offer:\n• Transportation and conveyance allowance\n• Employee stock options (ESOPs) for eligible roles\n• Professional development and training programs\n• Modern office with recreational facilities\n• Annual performance appraisal\n• Comprehensive health insurance for self and family\n• Salary Range: 7 LPA - 15 LPA per annum\n\nLocation: Pimpri-Chinchwad, Maharashtra, India\n\nIf you are excited about this opportunity, apply now and take the next step in your career journey with Celebi India International Enterprises!",
